@thalisvilela's suggestion worked for me.

My 'Android Gradle Plugin Version' is `4.2.2` and 'Gradle Version' is now `6.9.2`. I can now create image assets again.

Android studio is pestering me to take 'Android Gradle Plugin Version' right up to `7.2.2`. Anyone know if going that high is compatible with Flutter?
